Definitions
- "Software" means source code, binaries, and documentation covered by this license.
- "You" refers to any individual or entity obtaining a copy of the software.
- "Modified Version" means any functional, structural, or code-level alteration.

1. Grant of License
   You are granted a worldwide, royalty-free, non-exclusive license to:
   a) Use, copy, modify, merge the software;
   b) Distribute copies of the original or modified versions.

2. Restrictions
   a) NON-COMMERCIAL USE ONLY. Prohibited activities include:
      - Selling the software or commercial products containing it
      - Offering as paid service
      - Use in profit-generating activities
   b) For modified versions:
      - Must state "This is a modified version" prominently
      - Provide clear link to original software
      - YOU ASSUME ALL LEGAL LIABILITIES (e.g. data security violations, illegal content distribution)

3. User Compliance
   a) Must comply with laws of the People's Republic of China (Cybersecurity Law, Data Security Law)
   b) Prohibited: Distributing illegal content, disrupting network systems

4. Disclaimer & Liability
   a) Software provided "AS IS" without warranties
   b) IN NO EVENT SHALL COPYRIGHT HOLDERS BE LIABLE FOR DAMAGES (DATA LOSS, BUSINESS INTERRUPTION, ETC.)
   c) You shall defend against third-party claims from your use/modifications

5. Ownership & Termination
   a) All copyright and ultimate ownership remains with PrincipleCreativityOrg
   b) License terminates automatically upon violation

6. Governing Law
   This license is governed by laws of the People's Republic of China.
   Disputes shall be submitted to competent court in PrincipleCreativityOrg's location.

